snippet.title: Supersportic - Grandstand SD-070
snippet.description: Just flipping through the 10 different modes on this cartridge. I'm playing both paddles, so the gameplay isn't any good. The game itself is actually quite good With to players. Singleplayer training modes are not so entertaining.. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2013/07/supersportic-grandstand-sd-070.html
